        'Favicon Generator prepares a small icon for browser tabs, bookmarks, and saved shortcuts. It is useful when launching a site, prototype, blog, or product page.',
        'A favicon must remain recognizable at a very small size. Simple marks, initials, and bold shapes usually work better than detailed logos when many tabs are open.',
        'Favicon Generator is an essential tool when launching a new website or refreshing brand identity. A site without a favicon displays the browser default globe icon in its tab, giving an unfinished impression and making it harder to find among many open tabs or in a bookmark list.',
